Drag a board or robot here

Step 1 of 7 Open the "Boards" menu
Step 2 of 7 Select your board and drag it to the centre of the screen. (if you don't have a physical board, select the Freaduino UNO board)
Step 3 of 7 Drag the LED component and connect it to the board.
Step 4 of 7 You can now program the LED in the Software tab.
